[SHORT DESC]
Speed doubles in sun. 
[LONG DESC]
<p>Sun doubles the Speed of Pokémon with Chlorophyll. This is not a stat boost. If the sunlight ends or a new weather condition is brought into play, the Pokémon's Speed returns to normal.</p>
<h2>Related Abilities</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/abilities/swift_swim">Swift Swim</a> is a Rain equivalent.</p>